ANKARA , May 28 -LRB- Xinhua -RRB- -- Turkey Stressed respect to Iraq 's sovereignty and territorial integrity in an official statement issued here today .
The Turkish Foreign Ministry issued the statement following strong protests from neighboring Iraq and strong criticism from Iran , Syria and Arab and Western countries .
These countries demand an immediate withdrawal of the Turkish troops from northern Iraq .
The statement said that Turkey 's cross-border military operation , which is continuing in northern Iraq , is aimed at removing the terrorist danger toward Turkey from the vacant authority in the region .
<ENAMEX TYPE="OKAY">The goal of the military operation is to clear northern Iraq of all the rebels of the outlawed Kurdish Workers ' Party -LRB- PKK -RRB- , added the statement .</ENAMEX>
It said that like the previous cross-border military operations , Turkey will withdraw its security forces from the region as it reaches its goal to protect the life and security of the innocent people .
<ENAMEX TYPE="OKAY">With the support of air bombings and artillery fire , about 50,000-strong Turkish government troops have killed at least 1,800 PKK militants since Turkey launched the massive military operation in northern Iraq on May 14</ENAMEX> .
The military incursion followed a request for help by Iraq 's Kurdistan Democratic Party -LRB- KDP -RRB- Chairman Mesud Barzani , whose forces clashed with the PKK militants in northern Iraq .
